"4efae8a8-6ff1-47a0-8dbc-4891b1146af2", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"project": "public", "file_name": "How to Choose a Research Topic.pdf", "owner": "yash", "total_pages": 11, "file_path": "D:\\AIdata\\backend-api\\data\\yash\\public\\How to Choose a Research Topic.pdf", "source": "3"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": ["file_name", "file_type", "file_size", "creation_date", "last_modified_date", "last_accessed_date"], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": ["file_name", "file_type", "file_size", "creation_date", "last_modified_date", "last_accessed_date"], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "c3bab2a3-b99a-4008-8e30-ed2a269ac46a", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {"project": "public", "file_name": "How to Choose a Research Topic.pdf", "owner": "yash", "total_pages": 11, "file_path": "D:\\AIdata\\backend-api\\data\\yash\\public\\How to Choose a Research Topic.pdf", "source": "3"}, "hash": "b2920eea74664cd654f4fe0f38d01f748c30d31c018253eab2d8b35e139ccf84", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "CRICOS Provider Number: 03567C | Higher Education Provider Number: 14008 | RTO Provider Number: 51971\n\u2022\nPicking up a topic\n\u2022\nBeing flexible\n\u2022\nSearching for information\n\u2022\nNarrowing your topic\n\u2022\nReading, reading, reading\n\u2022\nBegin writing \nContents", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 0, "end_char_idx": 244, "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "1d1851bb-5dbf-4908-ae52-4ec309e9571d": {"__data__": {"id_": "1d1851bb-5dbf-4908-ae52-4ec309e9571d", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"project": "public", "file_name": "How to Choose a Research Topic.pdf", "owner": "yash", "total_pages": 11, "file_path": "D:\\AIdata\\backend-api\\data\\yash\\public\\How to Choose a Research Topic.pdf", "source": "4"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": ["file_name", "file_type", "file_size", "creation_date", "last_modified_date", "last_accessed_date"], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": ["file_name", "file_type", "file_size", "creation_date", "last_modified_date", "last_accessed_date"], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "98bf4cae-ed7d-4483-8168-6b587398e544", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {"project": "public", "file_name": "How to Choose a Research Topic.pdf", "owner": "yash", "total_pages": 11, "file_path": "D:\\AIdata\\backend-api\\data\\yash\\public\\How to Choose a Research Topic.pdf", "source": "4"}, "hash": "65e6a404a666752fe9a660260eb41f9d445d07390a516aa4cebaa726ffa2e112", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "CRICOS Provider Number: 03567C | Higher Education Provider Number: 14008 | RTO Provider Number: 51971\nTry to pick a topic that you find interesting. This will ensure the research \nprocess is as engaging and fun as possible.\nAsk yourself: What am I curious about? What questions do I have? What \ntopic would I like to learn more about? \nAlso consider: How long does my research paper need to be? Choose a \ntopic that seems appropriate for the length of the term/semester.\nGet inspiration: From previously completed projects at EIT and from \nscientific journals.\nPick a (manageable) Topic that Interests You", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 0, "end_char_idx": 605, "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "326b36ab-2079-4aa9-809d-234052c9206b": {"__data__": {"id_": "326b36ab-2079-4aa9-809d-234052c9206b", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"project": "public", "file_name": "How to Choose a Research Topic.pdf", "owner": "yash", "total_pages": 11, "file_path": "D:\\AIdata\\backend-api\\data\\yash\\public\\How to Choose a Research Topic.pdf", "source": "5"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": ["file_name", "file_type", "file_size", "creation_date", "last_modified_date", "last_accessed_date"], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": ["file_name", "file_type", "file_size", "creation_date", "last_modified_date", "last_accessed_date"], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "b5334784-7262-4636-a4b8-133038e40b02", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {"project": "public", "file_name": "How to Choose a Research Topic.pdf", "owner": "yash", "total_pages": 11, "file_path": "D:\\AIdata\\backend-api\\data\\yash\\public\\How to Choose a Research Topic.pdf", "source": "5"}, "hash": "fe8c63e7fcb0ffdc227899f39715acd08fd516e3aa7d10495c475389f34598d0", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "CRICOS Provider Number: 03567C | Higher Education Provider Number: 14008 | RTO Provider Number: 51971\nUnderstand that choosing a research \ntopic is a cyclical process. No topic \nshould be set in stone.\nBe prepared to change your topic as \nyou search for information, read \nabout your topic, and learn more.\nBe Flexible", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 0, "end_char_idx": 318, "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "450c95a9-7192-4e53-aa1d-2178a070b09b": {"__data__": {"id_": "450c95a9-7192-4e53-aa1d-2178a070b09b", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"project": "public", "file_name": "How to Choose a Research Topic.pdf", "owner": "yash", "total_pages": 11, "file_path": "D:\\AIdata\\backend-api\\data\\yash\\public\\How to Choose a Research Topic.pdf", "source": "6"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": ["file_name", "file_type", "file_size", "creation_date", "last_modified_date", "last_accessed_date"], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": ["file_name", "file_type", "file_size", "creation_date", "last_modified_date", "last_accessed_date"], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "35465a32-c0f4-46f8-9adb-54387d2ec8be", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {"project": "public", "file_name": "How to Choose a Research Topic.pdf", "owner": "yash", "total_pages": 11, "file_path": "D:\\AIdata\\backend-api\\data\\yash\\public\\How to Choose a Research Topic.pdf", "source": "6"}, "hash": "7926e4b55c2af2be3d854380848181c66b5dfa3cbd105cd1de111a9a8aa1b3c1", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "CRICOS Provider Number: 03567C | Higher Education Provider Number: 14008 | RTO Provider Number: 51971\nSearch for information resources, such as scholarly articles and books, in \nthe library catalogue and relevant databases. What do you find?\nIf you find too many information resources, your topic might be too broad. \nTo make your topic more specific and narrow, try to zero in on a single \naspect of your topic. \nSearch for Information on Your Topic", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 0, "end_char_idx": 450, "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "013b88e3-59d0-4009-8b1d-0c1b163b4de3": {"__data__": {"id_": "013b88e3-59d0-4009-8b1d-0c1b163b4de3", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"project": "public", "file_name": "How to Choose a Research Topic.pdf", "owner": "yash", "total_pages": 11, "file_path": "D:\\AIdata\\backend-api\\data\\yash\\public\\How to Choose a Research Topic.pdf", "source": "7"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": ["file_name", "file_type", "file_size", "creation_date", "last_modified_date", "last_accessed_date"], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": ["file_name", "file_type", "file_size", "creation_date", "last_modified_date", "last_accessed_date"], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "00f24f79-f522-4a61-bb71-2478a05ac5b6", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {"project": "public", "file_name": "How to Choose a Research Topic.pdf", "owner": "yash", "total_pages": 11, "file_path": "D:\\AIdata\\backend-api\\data\\yash\\public\\How to Choose a Research Topic.pdf", "source": "7"}, "hash": "70407134db6dfcf1dd814856aa66f8159e7900a7d0f5ad970b888590b677e151", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "CRICOS Provider Number: 03567C | Higher Education Provider Number: 14008 | RTO Provider Number: 51971\n\u2022 Could you focus on a more specific \nregion, time period, or group?\n \n\u2022 Could you focus on a specific aspect of \nyour topic? \n\u2022 Can you narrow your topic to a specific \nproblem or question? \nSome questions to ask yourself to help narrow your topic:", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 0, "end_char_idx": 351, "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "cc1e3bfd-a0a5-4d42-ae45-702b9f2663e2": {"__data__": {"id_": "cc1e3bfd-a0a5-4d42-ae45-702b9f2663e2", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"project": "public", "file_name": "How to Choose a Research Topic.pdf", "owner": "yash", "total_pages": 11, "file_path": "D:\\AIdata\\backend-api\\data\\yash\\public\\How to Choose a Research Topic.pdf", "source": "8"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": ["file_name", "file_type", "file_size", "creation_date", "last_modified_date", "last_accessed_date"], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": ["file_name", "file_type", "file_size", "creation_date", "last_modified_date", "last_accessed_date"], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "7351f789-34b0-41ad-bdaa-4ce6e7ba7ed0", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {"project": "public", "file_name": "How to Choose a Research Topic.pdf", "owner": "yash", "total_pages": 11, "file_path": "D:\\AIdata\\backend-api\\data\\yash\\public\\How to Choose a Research Topic.pdf", "source": "8"}, "hash": "44a6285222a2d0c5d7bd1cbd2c1db9fe6c4b85267d0501d157e168d78943ba49", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "CRICOS Provider Number: 03567C | Higher Education Provider Number: 14008 | RTO Provider Number: 51971\n\u2022\nIf you cannot find enough information resources, your topic might be too \nspecific. \n\u2022\nTo broaden your topic, consider removing some of your criteria from \nyour research topic. \nFor example, instead of investigating the use of self-driven cars by \nTransperth in Western Australia, you might broaden your topic to the use of \nself-driven cars in Australia. Alternatively, you might need to adjust the \nkeywords you have been using \u2013 talk to a librarian for help!\nNarrow your Topic and Search Again", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 0, "end_char_idx": 600, "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "5f986a6e-b2ba-4fa7-ae7e-18e679586bdc": {"__data__": {"id_": "5f986a6e-b2ba-4fa7-ae7e-18e679586bdc", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"project": "public", "file_name": "How to Choose a Research Topic.pdf", "owner": "yash", "total_pages": 11, "file_path": "D:\\AIdata\\backend-api\\data\\yash\\public\\How to Choose a Research Topic.pdf", "source": "9"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": ["file_name", "file_type", "file_size", "creation_date", "last_modified_date", "last_accessed_date"], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": ["file_name", "file_type", "file_size", "creation_date", "last_modified_date", "last_accessed_date"], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "c772b3b9-dc1f-4523-b643-7f4aedaf0688", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {"project": "public", "file_name": "How to Choose a Research Topic.pdf", "owner": "yash", "total_pages": 11, "file_path": "D:\\AIdata\\backend-api\\data\\yash\\public\\How to Choose a Research Topic.pdf", "source": "9"}, "hash": "0e4132d74d11558928c6ee09d789fdf4c1f724cd53f89d1098ea0fa0a7e9a361", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "CRICOS Provider Number: 03567C | Higher Education Provider Number: 14008 | RTO Provider Number: 51971\nabout your topic\n\u2022\nAs you read through your chosen information \nresources, you will learn more about your topic. \n\u2022\nIn response to what you learn, you may wish to \ntweak your topic further.\nDon\u2019t be afraid to change your topic to reflect what you read.\nRead", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 0, "end_char_idx": 359, "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "c3ba18e1-a3cf-4d0b-a4f1-396c3e304dc7": {"__data__": {"id_": "c3ba18e1-a3cf-4d0b-a4f1-396c3e304dc7", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"project": "public", "file_name": "How to Choose a Research Topic.pdf", "owner": "yash", "total_pages": 11, "file_path": "D:\\AIdata\\backend-api\\data\\yash\\public\\How to Choose a Research Topic.pdf", "source": "10"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": ["file_name", "file_type", "file_size", "creation_date", "last_modified_date", "last_accessed_date"], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": ["file_name", "file_type", "file_size", "creation_date", "last_modified_date", "last_accessed_date"], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "66f9c98b-89c4-41c2-9440-beeba6eb0fa8", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {"project": "public", "file_name": "How to Choose a Research Topic.pdf", "owner": "yash", "total_pages": 11, "file_path": "D:\\AIdata\\backend-api\\data\\yash\\public\\How to Choose a Research Topic.pdf", "source": "10"}, "hash": "d79f5ea91ff651f3ba7a3b71a4c654f6d36caa8bc27861fd1da346c79b509073", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "CRICOS Provider Number: 03567C | Higher Education Provider Number: 14008 | RTO Provider Number: 51971\n\u2022\nEven while you\u2019re writing, your topic may \nchange slightly. \n\u2022\nIn many ways, writing is a way of thinking \nthrough your topic. \nAs you write\u2014and think\u2014you may decide to refine your topic to better \nreflect the content of your research paper.\nBegin Writing", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 0, "end_char_idx": 359, "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "b27b8755-abfd-4cbc-a363-6270f9828255": {"__data__": {"id_": "b27b8755-abfd-4cbc-a363-6270f9828255", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"project": "public", "file_name": "How to Choose a Research Topic.pdf", "owner": "yash", "total_pages": 11, "file_path": "D:\\AIdata\\backend-api\\data\\yash\\public\\How to Choose a Research Topic.pdf", "source": "11"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": ["file_name", "file_type", "file_size", "creation_date", "last_modified_date", "last_accessed_date"], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": ["file_name", "file_type", "file_size", "creation_date", "last_modified_date", "last_accessed_date"], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "a9b6c178-3b8c-442a-b507-abe612d37d94", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {"project": "public", "file_name": "How to Choose a Research Topic.pdf", "owner": "yash", "total_pages": 11, "file_path": "D:\\AIdata\\backend-api\\data\\yash\\public\\How to Choose a Research Topic.pdf", "source": "11"}, "hash": "a376dd6ab07fc92e1de30e863ea4ae929380c3ff6466e294c12eacc2b1aa60b3", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "CRICOS Provider Number: 03567C | Higher Education Provider Number: 14008 | RTO Provider Number: 51971\nDon\u2019t worry. Keep in mind that the heart of your topic is still \nyour initial idea. \nThe tweaking and refining that occurs throughout the \nresearch process is simply a way of ensuring your topic is \nmanageable and accurately reflects the findings of your \nresearch.\nFeels like a Never-ending Story?", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 0, "end_char_idx": 400, "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}}}